message.entry: You cannot specify the "{0}" option more than once.
You can specify either "first" or "last" but not both.
You can specify either "sorted" or "stable" but not both.
You can specify either "legacy" or "R2012a" but not both.
You cannot specify "stable" and "sorted" with "first" and "last".
You cannot specify "stable" and "sorted" with "legacy" and "R2012a".
The "rows" input is not supported for cell array inputs.
Cell array input must be a cell array of character vectors.
Elements of cell array input A must be character vectors (row vectors of class char).
Input A must be a matrix in the "rows" case.
Unrecognized option. The only valid option is "rows".
